# Force LF line endings on checkout for all text files. Without this,
# Windows runners (`windows-latest` in CI) check out files with CRLF,
# which fails `prettier --check .` because the repo declares
# `endOfLine: lf` in `.prettierrc`. The `* text=auto eol=lf` rule keeps
# the working copy LF regardless of the platform's git config.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary blobs — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tgz binary
*.gz binary
